<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1904-06-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1904-06-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="671" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d671">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName>
                                to the <gloss type="to">King of Portugal</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">White
                                        House</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-06-13"><hi rend="italic">June 13,
                                1904</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I thank Your Majesty most sincerely for all your courtesy to me and
                            generous hospitality to our fleet, and beg to express my best wishes and
                            those of the American people for the health and happiness of Your
                            Majesty, and the prosperity of the people of Portugal.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Theodore
                            Roosevelt.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>